		{
			description: [
				"&eCobblemonRider&r lets you mount and ride compatible Cobblemon as living mounts — no saddle on a horse required."
				""
				"Not every Cobblemon is rideable. Larger species with suitable body shapes are compatible — check the CobblemonRider compatibility list to see which of your caught Cobblemon qualify."
				""
				"To mount, simply interact with a compatible Cobblemon in your party. Your first ride is the beginning of a much faster way to explore the world."
				""
				"&7Tip: Not all Cobblemon are rideable — check the compatibility list for your species.&r"
			]
