		{
			dependencies: ["1000000000000067"]
			description: [
				"Five hundred blocks on the back of a land mount. That's real distance — enough to cross a biome, explore a valley, and appreciate how much faster travel becomes."
				""
				"Ground and Normal types tend to make the fastest land mounts, with higher movement speed and better terrain handling. If your current mount feels slow, check your collection for a better candidate."
				""
				"Land mounts are your bread-and-butter travel option for most of the overworld. Get comfortable with riding."
				""
				"&7Tip: Larger Ground and Normal types tend to be the fastest land mounts.&r"
