		{
			dependencies: ["1000000000000067"]
			description: [
				"Flying mounts change everything. Where a land mount is fast, a flying mount is transformative — crossing mountains, oceans, and forests in a fraction of the time."
				""
				"Flying-type Cobblemon that are large enough to ride can carry you through the air. Launch from elevated ground for the best takeoff angle, and enjoy the view."
				""
				"Flying mounts are some of the most sought-after Cobblemon in the pack — if you don't have one yet, check your Cobblepedia for Flying types that spawn in accessible biomes."
				""
				"&7Tip: Launch from elevated ground for the best takeoff and most control.&r"
