			description: [
				"Cross an entire ocean biome on the back of a Water-type Cobblemon. No boat required."
				""
				"Water mounts can swim on the surface and dive underwater, letting you explore ocean floors, coral reefs, and underwater ruins without drowning. They breathe for you — just hang on."
				""
				"The ocean crossing itself is the challenge. Pick a direction, find a Water-type mount, and ride until you hit land on the other side."
				""
				"&7Tip: Water mounts can breathe underwater — use them to explore ocean floors for rare loot.&r"
